ed="T" n="0817a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0817a18"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023593"><placeName>洛陽</placeName><placeName>同德寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A004220">無名</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0817a19"/><persName key="A004220">釋無名</persName>，姓<name>高</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000022574">渤海</placeName>人也。祖宦今<placeName key="PL000000023603">西京</placeName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2252"/>，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0817a20"/>為<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>人矣。沖孺之齡，舉措卓異，口不嚌<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1110"/><lb
ed="T" n="0817a21"/>辛血，性不狎諠譁，邈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1112"/>矣出塵，故難留滯。<lb
ed="T" n="0817a22"/><date key="j19946531995036" from-iso="+0749-01-27" to-iso="+0750-02-14">年二十八</date>，若瘦雁<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1113"/>之出籠，投師習學，依隨<lb
ed="T" n="0817a23"/>隷<placeName key="PL000000023593">同德寺</placeName>。及精律藏，解一字以無疑；聞<lb
ed="T" n="0817a24"/>有禪宗，思千里而請決。舉領整裘，開扃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g673"/>見<lb
ed="T" n="0817a25"/>路，辭飛筆健，思若湧泉。因隨師遊方，訪祖<lb
ed="T" n="0817a26"/>師之遺跡，得<persName key="A005612">會<roleName>師</roleName></persName>付授心印<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1434"/>。<persName key="A005612">會</persName>先語諸徒<lb
ed="T" n="0817a27"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A005612">吾</ref>之付法，無有名字。」因號<persName key="A004220">無名</persName>也<ptr target="#n2253"/>。自此<lb
ed="T" n="0817a28"/>志歷四方，周遊<placeName key="PLG00000000002">五嶽</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬阜</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000016742">雙峯</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000015458"><anchor xml:id="beg0817sgsz1"/>𡷗<anchor xml:id="end0817sgsz1"/>公</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000014534"><anchor xml:id="beg0817sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>鑢</sic><corr>鑪</corr></choice><lb
ed="T" n="0817a29"/>嶺<anchor xml:id="end0817sgsz3"/></placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000008579">牛頭</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013448">剡溪</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013191">若耶</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明</placeName>，罔不<anchor xml:id="beg0817002"/>詢<anchor xml:id="end0817002"/>問，風<pb ed="T" n="0817b" xml:id="T50.2061.0817b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0817b01"/>格高遠，神操朗澈，博識者覩貌便伏，僻見<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1150"/>者<lb
ed="T" n="0817b02"/>發言必摧。時<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName>方納<persName key="A011933">鮮于叔明</persName>、<persName key="A011935">令狐峘</persName>料<lb
ed="T" n="0817b03"/>簡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1120"/>僧尼事<ptr target="#n2254"/>，時<persName key="A004220">名</persName>有表直諫，並停。尋時<persName key="A011933">鮮于<lb
ed="T" n="0817b04"/>叔明</persName>、<persName key="A011935">令狐峘</persName>等流<placeName key="PL000000030464">南海</placeName>百姓。至<date from-iso="+0790-01-24" key="j20096252010008" to-iso="+0791-02-11"><name>貞元</name>六年</date>，往<lb
ed="T" n="0817b05"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，居無定所。<date key="j20110842011084" when-iso="+0794-01-22">九年十二月十二日</date>於<lb
ed="T" n="0817b06"/><placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>先食訖，儼然坐化，春秋七十二，臘四<lb
ed="T" n="0817b07"/>十三。<date from-iso="+0795-01-30" key="j20114572011840" to-iso="+0796-02-17">十一年</date>闍維，獲舍利一升。<placeName key="PL000000004130">澤潞</placeName>節度使<lb
ed="T" n="0817b08"/><persName key="A010454">李抱真</persName>建塔於<placeName key="PL000000005371">佛光寺</placeName>，<date from-iso="+0790-01-24" key="j20096252010008" to-iso="+0791-02-11"><name>貞元</name>六年庚午歲</date>也<ptr target="#n2255"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0817b09"/>或云：「<persName key="A004220">名</persName>著疏解《彌陀經》<ptr target="#n1179"/>焉。」</p>
